    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-09-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-09-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="37" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d37">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Thompson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-09-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 8,
                            1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Gresham instructs Mr. Thompson to concert with other legations and make
                        by separate note representations to the Brazilian Government in regard to
                        the suspension of telegraphic intercourse, by which, especially at this
                        time, commerce suffers serious injury.</p>
            </div>
